						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">OneCrudeDude wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">How can you have a background scroll in the middle of something without the white moving around?</div><br />The same way a playfield scrolls without the status bar moving around: timed writes to the scrolling registers. But then I acknowledge that Drag's counterexample makes this technique slightly less reliable.</div>

